      Creates a new text input component
      Parameters:
      customId - The custom id of the component (max 100 characters)
      style - The TextInputStyle of the component
      label - The label of the component
      placeholder - The placeholder of the component
      value - The pre-filled value of the component
      minLength - The minimum length of the input (min 0, max 4000), default 0
      maxLength - The maximum length of the input (min 1, max 4000), default 4000
